                <table><tr><td width="75px">
                <img src="https://objectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/p/JqF1FqwGZL1LBG-ER-CJg2_Ev0-wrwnflP0I7dwc8d065zU6GvXWb9ORoqWvGncJ/n/c4u04/b/wms-storage/o/images/WMS-Logo-01-color.png" width="70px">
                </td><td>
                <p>To edit this workshop go back to the home page and click edit.  Only those who have appropriate roles can edit workshops (e.g. Stakeholder, Workshop Team, Publisher teams, etc). <br><br>You can email the workshop team from this page if you need to contact them.</p>
                </td></tr></table>
                ```
