    pageItem P14_GREEN_BUTTON_REQ (
        type: richTextEditor
        label {
            label: Green Button Requirements
            alignment: left
        }
        settings {
            format: html
            minHeight: 180
        }
        layout {
            sequence: 150
            region: @livelabs-publishing
            slot: regionBody
            alignment: left
        }
        appearance {
            template: @optional-above
            templateOptions: #DEFAULT#
        }
        source {
            formRegion: @workshop-details
            column: GREEN_BUTTON_REQ
            dataType: clob
        }
        default {
            type: static
            staticValue:
                ```
                <b> Please fill out our Green Button Questionnaire to determine if this workshop can be run on a registered LiveLabs Tenancy.  <br><br>If your workshop is in production already, copy this text and submit it via Chat with the Workshop Team and we will process. </b>
                <br/> <br/> 
                <u>BASIC QUESTIONS</u><br>
                <ul>
                <li><b>1. Do you have a Tenancy or the approved budget to purchase cloud credits? </b> Yes/No </b></li>
                <li><b>2. Are you in DB Product Management? </b> Yes/No </b></li>
                <li><b>3. Do you need Cloud Shell access? </b> Yes/No </b></li>
                <li><b>4. Do you need a compute instance (Linux is by default) </b>  Yes or No</li>
                <li><b>5. OCI - List of Policies: </b> Enter the list of policies here</li>
                <li><b>6. Do you have an existing Terraform script? </b> Yes or No</li>
                <li><b>7. Do you have an existing Shell/Python/CLI Scripts? </b> Enter them here</li> </ul>
                
                <br/> <u>NETWORK QUESTIONS</u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. OCI - Is VCN Required? </b>  Yes or No</li> 
                <li><b>2. Do you need the user to modify the VCN?  </b> Yes or No</li>
                <li><b>3. Are any other port openings required other than 22? If so list them here. (This request may be subject to CSSAP approval) </b> Yes or No</li> </ul>
                
                <br/> <u>IMAGES AND THE MARKETPLACE</u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. Do you need an image installed and started on compute (DB 19c, EM, Golden Gate, etc)? </b>Enter here </li>
                <li><b>2. Is the image already in Marketplace? <i>If no, the image needs to be submitted to marketplace in order to proceed, attend Office Hours</i> </b> Yes or No</li>  </ul>
                
                <br/> <u>OKE </u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. Do you need an OKE cluster </b>  Yes or No</li>
                <li><b>2. How many nodes? </b> Enter here</li></ul>
                
                <br/> <u>DATA SCIENCE</u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. Do you need a Data Science service? </b> Answer Here</li> 
                <li><b>2. Dynamic group required?</b> Yes or No</li> </ul>
                
                <br/> <u>DATA SAFE</u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. Do you need Data Safe Service? </b> Yes or No</li>  </ul>
                
                <br/> <u>ADDITIONAL SERVICES AND QUESTIONS</u><br>
                <ul><li><b>1. What additional resources/services do you need that aren''t listed above: </b>Enter here</li>
                <li><b>2. Object Storage </b> Enter Size</li>Size
                <li><b>3. Block Storage</b> Enter Size</li>
                <li><b>4. Container Repo</b> Add details here</li> </ul>
                
                <br/> <br/> <b>Any Additional requirements? </b> Enter them here
                <br/> <br/> <br/> --------------------------------NOTES FROM LIVELABS ADMIN--------------------------------<br>(For Official Use Only)<br>
                ```
        }
        security {
            encryptSessionState: false
        }
    )

